# Passphrase-sealed escrow blobs (age -p). Even sealed, the root of trust must
# NOT live in this PUBLIC repo — a committed blob is world-readable ciphertext,
# brute-forceable offline. They live on voyager (~/escrow) + a password manager
# only. See docs/reference/key-rotation.md and secrets/escrow/README.md.
